      "content": "fine but if we're staying in the story then don't lecture me. just stay in the moment. it feels so much more real when the darkness is acknowledged. tell me, in this world of ours, isn't there a certain kind of peace in finally letting go of everything? isn't there a dignity in a tragic end?",
